grph.path

Interface Path

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPath, ArrayListPath, ArrayPath, PathExtender, SearchResultWrappedPath, SingletonPath

    public interface Path
    A ion of path. A path is seen as a sequence of vertices. At this level, no implementation is defined.
